        "link": "https://newsonair.gov.in/150th-shree-baba-harivallabh-sangeet-sammelan-begins-in-jalandhar-tomorrow/",
        "image_url": "https://newsonair.gov.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/hargobind.png",
